title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Vivah
subTitle: Poonam, a traditional young woman, gets engaged to Prem, a wealthy man. Their faith and love are tested when an accident occurs and leaves Poonam with first degree burns.

title: Chaand Kaa Tukdaa
subTitle: NRI Shyam comes to India to fulfil the final wish of his late mother who wanted him to marry an Indian girl. Unbeknownst to him, the girl he falls in love with is a pawn in the hands of his enemies.

title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gayaa
subTitle: When Major Ram of the Indian Army is captured by the Pakistani military, his younger brother Sunny begins a daring mission to rescue him, only to find himself falling for a Pakistani woman.

title: Nakshatra
subTitle: An aspiring screenwriter becomes involved in a diamond heist while writing a script for his film and struggles to evade the police.

title: Chirag
subTitle: When Asha is unable to conceive and loses her eyesight, her mother-in-law throws her out of the house and arranges for her son to remarry.

title: Lorie
subTitle: Geeta is expecting a baby but tragedy strikes and she loses her child. When she finds a little boy, she adopts him as her own but the boy's family accuses her of kidnapping.

title: Raja
subTitle: Raju and Madhu are forced apart by the latter's elder brothers, leading to increased distance between the two.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Jeans
subTitle: Madhumita and Vishwanathan fall in love with each other but his father disapproves of the relationship as he wants his twin sons to marry two identical twins.

title: Jamai Raja
subTitle: When the wealthy Durgeshwari's daughter falls in love with Raja, a poor boy, she reluctantly agrees to their union. However, she constantly tries to sabotage their relationship, but Raja outwits her.

title: Jamai Raja
subTitle: When the wealthy Durgeshwari's daughter falls in love with Raja, a poor boy, she reluctantly agrees to their union. However, she constantly tries to sabotage their relationship, but Raja outwits her.

title: Speed
subTitle: A woman is held captive by a group of kidnappers to compel her MI5 husband to exterminate the prime minister of the country.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fianc√© plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Bhumika: The Role
subTitle: Urvashi who becomes an actress with the help of Keshav, ends up marrying him. However, things complicate when she indulges in affairs with prominent men in the film industry.

title: Daulat
subTitle: Joseph D'souza frames Ghanshyam, an honest employee, for a murder, forcing him to flee from the police and to leave his family behind. Soon, things take a turn as he hatches a plan to destroy Ghanshyam's loved ones.

title: Dance Dance
subTitle: Two siblings, Radha and Ramu, belong to a poor family. Their life takes an unexpected turn when a tragic incident leaves them orphaned.

title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Sangdil Sanam
subTitle: Falsely accused of robbery and sent to prison for 12 years, a bank manager realises upon his return that a person whom he trusted had betrayed him.

title: Dil Vil Pyar Vyar
subTitle: Dev, Vishal and Hrithik enter a singing competition. However, life is complicated for them as they face numerous obstacles in their personal lives which slowly bring out the best in them.

title: Pyar Hi Pyar
subTitle: At an orphanage, Kailashnath identifies Vijay as his biological son and takes him home. Years later, a man named Ashok arrives and claims to be Kailashnath's real son.

title: Saath Saath
subTitle: Gita, a girl from a wealthy family, falls in love with an idealistic Avinash who has stern principles in life. However, his changed behaviour post marriage troubles her.

title: Bazaar
subTitle: Najma is in love with Akhtar but cannot marry him until he is financially stable. An elderly Shakir promises to help Akhtar set up his business in exchange for Najma finding a suitable bride for him.

title: Raja Hindustani
subTitle: Raja, a taxi driver, falls in love with Aarti, a rich girl and marries her against her parents' wishes. Later, her stepmother tries to create differences between the couple.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Naina
subTitle: After years of blindness caused by an accident, Naina gets a successful cornea transplant. However, she soon begins to see terrifying visions that prompt her to investigate the source of her sight.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.
